    "2026-04-16": {
      "lines": [
        "I listened to my audiobook “the mountain is you”. ",
        "Healing is usually thought of as peaceful and enjoyable and comfortable but it is the complete opposite ",
        "Healing your mind is different than healing your body. You’re gutting yourself and becoming new. \n\nHealing the body puts you back into a previous state, while healing mentally/emotionally is totally new transformation into something new ",
        "You do not find resolutions in avoiding the problem. ",
        "",
        "",
        "",
